arChildNodes.szComment: Neyrelle drops to her knees beside Akarat. She strokes his face.
The lion spasms, coughing and chuffing.

The Lion spasms and shifts, fading into golden wisps of dust and light. Soon a recognizable figure takes shape - the human spirit form of AKARAT.

Akarat is on one knee, exhausted. His sword tumbles to the ground in front of him with a loud metallic thud. 

Player takes a step back as Neyrelle gets to her feet, looking down at him.
Akarat is lifted/pulled into the air
Neyrelle reaches up to him but doesn’t touch him. A glowing light gathers behind Akarat and he turns to walk into it. Neyrelle stops him with a word.
There is a moment of silence.
